TITLE: Episode 13 - May the Force Be Gayer
DESCRIPTION: This week, we examine the newest Star Wars movie, The Rise of Skywalker's amount of gay on the Gayest of Scales, talk about gender pronouns and burgerless burgers and Tennessee's General Assembly's bill that would require students to play sports based on the gender assigned on their birth certificates.
